Package: gdalcli
Title: A Generative R Frontend for the GDAL (>= 3.11) Unified CLI
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Author", "Name", email = "author@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive, auto-generated R wrapper for the modern GDAL unified CLI (RFC 104).
    Combines lazy evaluation (inspired by dbplyr) with process-isolated state management
    to deliver a composable, pipe-aware interface for raster and vector processing.
    Supports file-less I/O streaming via VSI handlers and includes helpers for GDAL Virtual
    File System URL composition across 30+ cloud, archive, and utility handlers.
